This is a link to the Limelight Documentation on your question. When you refer the “target width in pixels” you are looking for the thor NetworkTable value. The code below should return the horizontal length of the target in pixels.

NetworkTableInstance.getDefault().getTable(“limelight”).getEntry(“thor”).getDouble(0);

If you are unsure of how to use the values from the limelight, check out the study cases in the Limelight docs.
